description: Corey Fryia is a Canadian comic book writer. He is the writer/co-creator of Doctor Crowe from 215 Ink. Corey also served as a co-editor on Out of the Blue: An Anthology of Strange Stories as well as Out of the Blue: A Collection of Campfire Talesfrom Stache Publishing and has written and contributed to various other independent anthologies and publications. Corey currently resides in South Central Kentucky with his two dogs, an amazing wife and an unhealthy obsession with all things Star Wars.
name: Corey Fryia
